Package: agentdr
Version: 0.2.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: CoSAI Community <agentdr@cosai.dev>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31)
Homepage: https://github.com/girdav01/agentdr
Description: AgentDR — AI Agent Detection & Response
 Endpoint agent that monitors local AI runtimes (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex,
 Aider, OpenClaw, etc.), accepts OpenTelemetry signals on the loopback OTLP
 endpoint, inventories and intercepts Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers,
 and ships normalised CoSAI AI Telemetry Framework events (OCSF Category 7)
 to any SIEM.
